# Git Operation Rules
tags: ["git", "safety", "validation"]
appliesTo: ["CursorAgent", "GPT", "Ghost"]
enforce: true
priority: critical

## Rules

- Never use `--force` without explicit user approval.
- Never push to `main` unless validated and approved by GPT.
- Never merge to `main` without GPT validation.
- All commits must pass lint + typecheck before being tagged.